summary: My favorite part of Detective Pikachu’s design isn’t just how damned cute he looks, but the fact that they added a white patch...
body:
My favorite part of Detective Pikachu’s design isn’t just how damned cute he looks, but the fact that they added a white patch on his belly like how Pikachu had one in the Red and Blue games.

It’s this kind of attention to detail that should not be ignored. We really need to stop sleeping on this.

summary: I don’t know if there will be more live action Pokemon movies
body:
I don’t know if there will be more live action Pokemon movies

But I want an adaptation of Chimchar’s arc during the Sinnoh anime. Give me an abused ape who gets a new partner, and through love and kindness Chimchar becomes one of the strongest Pokemon in all of Sinnoh. Maybe have part of the conflict be the war between the Gods in the animated Sinnoh movies, comparing the primate’s helplessness and attempts to impress his old partner with the apathy and callousness of the Gods to both humans and Pokemon. And well, Infernape is based off Sun Wukong, I feel like he should wage war against heaven.
